introduction: Overview (1)Height	 5' 2" (1.57 m)Mini Bio (1)Cricket was from Tipp City, Ohio but now loves living in Los Angeles for her to follow her dream in becoming a successful actress. She has worked on numerous Commercials as well as a recurring Guest Star role on the hit show "About a Boy".
